text: Catapausa sulcatipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1950. It is known from the Solomon Islands.BioLib.cz - Catapausa sulcatipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1950
